dct_title_s: A map of California with descriptive notes
dct_description_sm: National Geographic Society Oblique cylindrical projection. Inset maps: San Diego (1:190,000), Yosemite Valley (1:63,360), Los Angeles (1:380,160), San Francisco (1:42,240), San Fransisco Bay Region (1:380,160). Issued with the National Geographic magazine, v. 105, no. 6, June 1954.
